1.Third-party Management - Incorporate ISO 27701’s detailed requirements for third-party data processors to ensure all aspects of privacy and security are covered.
2.Audit Frequency - Align with the revised policy's bi-annual audits, adopting ISO 27701's detailed privacy considerations.
3.Policy Review Cycle - Maintain the quarterly review cycle, integrating ISO 27001’s risk management framework to ensure rapid response to evolving threats and compliance requirements.
4.Proactive Threat Management - Utilize the structured risk assessment approach of ISO 27001 along with the advanced threat detection technologies proposed in the revised policy.
